  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>僕達にはエターナルソードが必要なんだ。
渡してくれないか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We need the Eternal Sword.
Will you hand it over?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それは……出来ません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I... can't do that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんでだよ！
お前達にオレ達の邪魔をする
権利なんてあんのかよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why not?! What, do you guys think you
have the right to get in our way like this?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>今のエターナルソードは
使っちゃいけないんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You can't use the Eternal Sword right now!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どうしても渡せねぇってなら
力ずくで奪うまでだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you won't hand the Eternal Sword over,
we'll take it by force!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>気は進まないけど……仕方がないね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't want to do this... but we have to.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ダメなんだ！
今のエターナルソードは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dammit! The Eternal Sword is...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
